<p>I really like this. Lots of good detail.</p>
<p>That helicopter thing, man. Fuck. And Stevenson. Great stuff.</p>
<p>One nitpick:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>The final photo showed a [REDACTED].</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Pretty bullshit redaction - it doesn't imply anything except that 'there is something interesting here which the author decided to keep from me for no reason, OR the author was lazy and wanted to add cheap mystery factor here'.</p>
<p>Besides that&#8230; I don't like where it ends. <em>I really want more.</em> I also think that:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Further surveys of an area within 1 sq. km. of the warehouse are preemptively denied.</p>
</blockquote>
