<p>I want to upvote, but I agree with all the notes from Howell2010, and I gotta downvote. It has huge potential- reminds me of the &quot;lost hour&quot; from Eerie Indiana- but it falls short. I don't expect an older SCP to be fixed, but if it is, I'll upvote.</p>

